00\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1628930/extras/92ce49634ba034119e623f1a2ee09779.mp4?t=1633707700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Some Items to Help You On Your Journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1628930/extras/50904d5a489e850482fed801aa71ec2c.poster.avif?t=1633707700\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1628930/extras/50904d5a489e850482fed801aa71ec2c.webm?t=1633707700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1628930/extras/50904d5a489e850482fed801aa71ec2c.mp4?t=1633707700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game has 45 different challenges that will test your memory and reasoning.",
